                      CHAPTER 96</span></div></div><br clear="all"/><div id="title"><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:0.9em;">An act to add and repeal Chapter 5 (commencing with Section 21400) of Division 21 of the Elections Code, relating to redistricting, and declaring the urgency thereof, to take effect immediately.</span></div><br clear="all"/><div align="center">
                  
                  [<span style="  font-size: 1.3em">
                Approved  by
